    {
        "content": "<p>[answering to the deleted post] The abstract of the paper linked by Sebastien says that they have partitions of unity too. I'm going to formalize the weak Whitney embedding thm soon, then revive this paper with this thm as a selling point (unless the actual Isabelle library has it; I'll look into this tomorrow).</p>",
